@startuml level2_two_agents
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam defaultFontName "Segoe UI"
skinparam defaultFontSize 12
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundCorner 10

title **Level 2 — Two Agents (Basic Split)**

|Client|
start
:Submit business question;

|#E8F5E9|Consultant Agent|
:Receive client question;
:Conduct full research & analysis;
:Write consulting report;

|#FFF3E0|Evaluator Agent|
:Receive final report;
:Score **Completeness** (1-10);
:Score **Accuracy** (1-10);
:Score **Coherence** (1-10);
:Score **Structure** (1-10);
:Produce evaluation scorecard;

|Client|
:Receive report + evaluation;
stop

@enduml
